e an interlocutor in his own thoughts.\r\nWhich, however, does not touch you in the country,\r\nwhere is smaller ahead than behind.\r\nBranst the guitar.The streets are overoxy.\r\nA passerby is drowning in a yellow veil. Inxing the pond, everything has become much overgrown.\r\nMissing and lizards are teeming.In crowns\r\nBirds swirl with and without eggs.\r\nThat destroys all dynasties - the number\r\nHeirs with a lack of thrones.\r\nAnd the elections and forest are coming.I would not recognize the area.From niches\r\nBusts disappeared, the porticoes were dry,\r\nThe wall settled with gums in the ravine.\r\nYou will saturate your eyes, but you can’t lengthen the thought.\r\nGardens and parks go to the jungle.\r\nAnd involuntarily breaks down from the lips: cancer.	Бродский Иосиф	https://poemata.ru/poets/brodskiy-iosif/guernavaka/	0	2023-01-20 07:05:19.242432
