d.In reply\r\nHe kisses her lips\r\nSqueezes her a corset.\r\nCool evening,\r\nBreathes on her face on a bow\r\nAnd strong tobacco. On Basket is unaccounted for\r\nThe brooch is cracking\r\nWith your sweaty hand, -\r\nAttracts into a thick rye. Molly.Under the trill of frogs\r\nShe is sweet, sweet to be sweet.\r\nOn the face of golden freckles\r\nThe tan sprinkled the network. The sequic breath gently\r\nIn the tuning of mowers.\r\nDoes not see them, does not hear\r\nFather Archpriest.\r\nHe pressed to the window:\r\nCrushing with a cruel word\r\nSubmissive wife. "Again left the case\r\nWalk a native daughter.\r\nI didn’t look again! ”\r\nAnd looks - looks at the night. And he sees through the hazel\r\nIn evening purity\r\nOnly the sky and a birdhouse\r\nOn a bent pole.\r\nHe is scolding all night,\r\nFlying stream\r\nLightning is lightened.\r\nSeday to the hollow\r\nAnd dark icons\r\nZarya is already golden. And there is a love game there,\r\nThe stoop of the shaggy sheet,\r\nAbove the pale Popular\r\nSeminarist is inclined.\r\nNettle and burdock.\r\nScreaming in dawn smoke\r\nDocumentary rooster. School of river put the tops\r\nIn foggy reeds.\r\nMay the sick sickle fade\r\nHanging in clouds.	Белый Андрей	https://poemata.ru/poets/belyy-andrey/popovna/	0	2023-01-20 07:05:19.242432
