ll\r\nIn the run -in the groove and in the compression of the nucleus,\r\nFor indifferent\r\nFluid water and hot fog\r\nDali the muscle\r\nRunning legs and whirlwinds,\r\nFor the fact that in the self -war\r\nAir of air\r\nWeoned the nest with the rebellious spirits of the explosion,\r\nFor the fact that greed ores\r\nThey turned the iron spiders into the army,\r\nInexorably weaving\r\nSucking and strangling threads -\r\nFor that I free\r\nCaptured demons\r\nFrom the oaths of humility,\r\nAnd chaos compressed in the vortices of the substance\r\nAnd in the dance of the whirlwinds\r\nFrom the formation of music!\r\nI give them power over the world,\r\nSo far, people\r\nThey will not win them again\r\nSelf -humble and won\r\nAnger, greed, self -willed, indifferent ... ”3rd demon abyss exclaimed, mocking:\r\n“The curse of Babylon is being removed!\r\nLanguages in a section\r\nThe end came: the same speeches\r\nLive in the lips of enemies,\r\nBut the meaning of the names and the capacity of words\r\nI distorted inside.\r\nUnderstanding, but the tongue became confused\r\nBlessedly.Everyone thinks\r\nThe war to kill the war\r\nAnd defeat cruelty by cruelty.\r\nAnd the martyr will multiply with his truth\r\nMy lies.\r\nWisdom,\r\nShamelessly exposed like a harlot,\r\nCaresses warriors\r\nAnd the truths that have gone crazy\r\nFrozen, sliding along the puddles\r\nGlacial blood.Man,\r\nReached consent in everything,\r\nThere is nothing else left\r\nHow to destroy each other to the end! ”4 I saw: the doors of the sky opened\r\nIn the constellation Leo, and demons\r\nThey rushed to the ground.\r\nLeaving houses\r\nPeople in river valleys crowded,\r\nMeaning the great kingdoms of the boundaries,\r\nAnd, tearing in the ground\r\nThe moves of snakes and mouse paths,\r\nGround herds of voracious monsters:\r\nYourself\r\nAnd shepherds and food. 5. It seemed as if overturned\r\nAnd not baptized by the waters of the flood\r\nThe world seemed: they crawled out of Tina\r\nHuge crankshaf