ue happiness,\r\nHe is close to unfortunately\r\nWho does not value time - to oblivion,\r\nThe Prophet echoed us:\r\n“Do not forget the lesson -\r\nWho owes everyone to their appearance. ”\r\nI see snow -white glare in a dream,\r\nLike a swarm of the web, enveloping me,\r\nTorture, as if they would look for confessions,\r\nForgetting that they tamed me for a long time.\r\nI hear the cry of Aligoria so clearly\r\nLike a slogan of prayers memorized\r\nWho will become lambs in the slaughter of God,\r\nAnd who is a powerful autocrat ...\r\nWhen would we cherish our culture,\r\nWithout letting the vice to land,\r\nOur heads on the areas of thought,\r\nDo not let the evil rock sound ...\r\nA great victory that humanity knows,\r\nVictory is not over death, and believe, not over fate,\r\nThe judge counted you that the heavenly court judges,\r\nOnly one victory is a victory over yourself.	Омар Хайям	https://poemata.ru/poets/hayyam-omar/bytuet-mnenie-chto-schaste-eto-dar/	0	2023-01-20 07:05:19.242432
