se, as in the days of the past,\r\n_Y rolled waves of blue,\r\n_Y shine with proud beauty! .. Fifteen years old\r\nViolence in Western captivity;\r\nYou did not give up and grumbled\r\nBut the hour struck - the violence fell:\r\nIt went like a key to the bottom.\r\nYour Wave your native Rus'\r\nAnd to the disagreement of the one that God will judge\r\nThe great Sevastopol wakes up\r\nFrom an enchanted sleep. And that you are during it\r\nFrom the swearing hid the bad weather\r\nIn his sympathetic bosom,\r\nYou will give us- and without damage-\r\nImmortal Black Sea Fleet. Yes, in the heart of the Russian people\r\nThis day will be sown-\r\nHe is our external freedom,\r\nHe is the Peter and Paul Code\r\nThe grave canopy will illuminate ... the beginning of March 1871* A. S. Pushkin.	Тютчев Федор	https://poemata.ru/poets/tyutchev-fedor/chernoe-more/	0	2023-01-20 07:05:19.242432
