s in it -\nI walked on him by heart.\nI dived into his lane,\nWhere once Love lost.\nI was looking, I wandered to dark.\nBut she did not meet anywhere,\nBut she did not meet anywhere.\nI left the city at midnight home.\nHe flew outside the window.He accompanied me.\n...	Р. Рождественский	https://www.culture.ru/poems/42621/ekho-pervoi-lyubvi	6	2023-09-08 10:32:12.960001
