th a black mustache\r\nstands back under the gate\r\nand scratches with dirty hands\r\nUnder a dirty hat, your nape,\r\nAnd the window is heard in the windows\r\nAnd the clatter of the legs and the ringing of bottles. 14 Oct, 1933.	Хармс Даниил Иванович	https://poemata.ru/poets/harms-daniil/postoyanstvo-veselya-i-gryazi/	0	2024-10-11 09:03:02.24425
